Package com.autonomy.aci.client.annotations

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IdolAnnotationsProcessorFactory
    Factory for producing IdolAnnotationsProcessors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IdolAnnotationsProcessorFactoryImpl
    Default implementation of IdolAnnotationsProcessorFactory.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FieldType
    Enum representing possible types for the values of the annotations.
    ValueType
    Enum that determines how an annotation value will be resolved.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    IdolBuilder
    Designates a static inner class as a builder for its outer class.
    IdolBuilderBuild
    Designates the target method as the build method for a given IdolBuilder.
    IdolDocument
    Optional annotation used to designate a class as having IDOL annotations.
    IdolField
    Indicates that a method should be called with the result of an IDOL field.
    IdolProcessorField
    Indicates that when the given IDOL field is reached a StAXProcessor with the given class should be called.
